title: Body-Solid BSTWPBOX 3-in-1 Wooden Plyo Box
description:
*Exercise performed on BSTWPBOX 3-in-1 Wooden Plyo Box: 

The Body-Solid BSTWPBOX 3-in-1 Wooden Plyo Box features three distinct height options making it the perfect plyo box for fitness enthusiasts of all levels while giving you the advantage of three plyo boxes in one.

Designed for use in both home and commercial settings, the BSTWPBOX is ideal for several exercises including box jumps, dips, step-ups, negative jumps, box push-ups and more.

Features include on-product exercise instruction showing the correct way to perform plyo box movements and exercises. Constructed from high-quality wood, the BSTWPBOX is durable enough to hold up during even the most intense of workouts.

Sanded edges and a slip-free surface offer superior and safe landing grip while preventing falls and slips and helping avoid harsh scrapes and bruises.
